        "description": {
            "value": "<p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\"><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">You form a ball of acid between your hands and hurl it. It bursts on impact with the ground and melts nearby creatures.</em></span></p><p><strong>Dexterity Save</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure</strong>:\u00a0Target takes [[/damage 1d8 acid]]\u00a0damage.*</p></li><li><p><strong>Success</strong>:\u00a0No damage.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">*At Higher Levels:</strong> This spell's damage increases by 1d8 when you reach a total character or creature level of 5th level ([[/damage 2d8 acid]]), 11th level ([[/damage 3d8 acid]]), and 17th level ([[/damage 4d8 acid]]).</span></p>",
